title: Hawkwind - Pacific Arts Centre, Birkenhead - 15th December, 2005
description:
Hawkwind - Pacific Arts Centre, Birkenhead - 15th December, 2005

One of the best quality audience recordings I&#039;ve ever heard.

Enjoy the show.
